Serendipity 'Google Quicksearch' Plug-in
by Wesley Hwang-Chung, version 1.3

This plug-in enables you to add quicksearch functionality to your s9y blog that uses Google engine instead of the default database querying. For best results, use in conjunction with Google AdSense service.

History
1.3: Fixed XHTML validation issue; added 'submit' button option
1.2: Better support for non-AdSense ('Free') version
1.1: Initial Release
